So we were down to your main research interests.  And regarding this South London research, I wanted to ask you what it was like for yo}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid6957381 u, working interdisciplinarily?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 
