\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid7229103 Sandra:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid94135\charrsid8210080 \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid94135\charrsid8210080 The sequences are \'85
 I think that that first London Study was a sort of watershed in the sense that after that, it was always about the kind of dynamic of a mixed population, how do people get by in difficult circumstances?  Wh
at are the strategies which they use?  How amazing they are in terms of sheer survival, sometimes.  So that although each one had its own stated objective, for me, in my head, one flows from the other, and it\rquote 
s usually about what are the options in this area, or in this circumstance?  Who takes up the options?  How do people manage a livelihood, and what do they regard as a decent livelihood?  Yeah, I think that applies in virtually all of them, and I\rquote 
