t held. So I think that was useful.  I think that was useful in setting out the sort of context, you know, what else is happening?  Wh
at else is happening besides women not getting their infections treated, was a whole hospital thing.  And none of it is necessarily stuff that people didn\rquote 
t know already.  I think one has to recognise that the useful thing, sometimes, is that you can bring all the bits together, and say, \'93This is how they relate to each other\'94.  But there\rquote 
s somebody out there who knows each of the bits, maybe different people know each of the bits, but if one can manage to bring it together, and say, \'93Well, this is the whole package.  This is how i}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
